snippet.title: Amber Heard facing 4 years of Jail time? | Finally Justice For Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
In this video, we are going to share the latest update on amber heard. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
________________________________________________________

The Johnny Depp and Amber Heard courtroom drama took a major plot twist when Johnny Depp sued his ex-wife for libel. He not only claimed that she lied in court, but also that she abused him. However, the actors will have to wait even longer for an official court ruling. If the court rules in favor of Johnny Depp, Amber Heard could face up to three years in prison.
